    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay fine but its getting kind of scary. my chest feels kinda tight and i feel a bit lightheaded too. maybe it is just the humidity like u said? if i just stay in the AC and try some herbal tea or something to relax my lungs instead of going to the hospital, u think that would work? it's probably just a panic attack or something right?",
